@startuml
title User Reporting an Account

|User|
start
:Open report account option;
:Select report reason;
:Enter report details;
:Submit report;

|System|
:Validate report data;

while (Report invalid?) is (Yes)
  :Display validation error message;
  |User|
  :Correct report information;
  :Resubmit report;
  |System|

endwhile (No)

:Store report in database;
:Notify administrator;

|Marketplace Administrator|
:Review report;

if (Violation confirmed?) then (Yes)
  |System|
  :Ban or reach out to reported user account;
  :Log moderation action;
  :Mark report as resolved;
else (No)
  |System|
  :Dismiss report;
  :Mark report as closed;
  :Log review outcome;
endif

end
@enduml